Description: 'IR Compound Full - runs tool verification plus the official/stock KAPE modules that cover every artifact confirmed present in a Windows.KapeFiles.Targets (_KapeTriage/_SANS_Triage) Velociraptor collection, instead of maintaining bespoke duplicates of tools KAPE already ships modules for. Uses FileMask/%sourceFile% and tool-internal recursive -d scanning wherever available, so it does not need to know the exact device-root folder name Velociraptor encodes into uploads\ntfs\<device> / uploads\auto\<device> - point msource at <CollectionRoot>\uploads directly (Run-IRParse.ps1 does this for you). Output lands in each referenced module''s own native Category subfolder (FileSystem, Registry, ProgramExecution, EventLogs, FileFolderAccess, WebBrowsers, FileDeletion, SRUMDatabase, SUMDatabase), not a custom numbered scheme.'
Category: IR
Author: ir-endpoint-investigations
Version: 2.0
Id: 6f1a2b3c-4d5e-4f60-8a1b-2c3d4e5f6a7b
BinaryUrl: https://github.com/EricZimmerman/KAPE
ExportFormat: csv
